# |    Function f_menu_server_action_gui   |
# +----------------------------------------+
#
#  Inputs: $1=GUI - "dialog" or "whiptail" The CLI GUI application in use.
#          $2=Server name.
#    Uses: CHOICE_ACT, PASSWORD, MENU_TITLE.
